d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"我意思係冇收你額外費用？<br />\n例如鑽牆果d"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:01:08.000Z","msg":"佢基本安裝包哂，佢上黎睇位就收100，但搵佢裝就會之後減返，你當落訂咁囉，如果你條去水喉要加槽遮住啲喉先要加錢<br />\n我記得本身只係包鑽一個窗口窿，佢最後鑽咗兩個都冇收多我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEw6jab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEw6jab.jpg&h=e98cf4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWRBGox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWRBGox.jpg&h=bdec5898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n協興？ 睇佢fb啲圖裝工普通啦，唔算差嘅，但都係兩條銅喉同電線包埋一條豬腸，電線室外嗰part有入膠喉算有良心。<br />\n收費貴左啲啲，但佢包15尺，連訊號線添，好多店只包12尺，如果用盡15尺就抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話黑色豬腸要加錢，即係唔係用armaflex，唔知加錢轉黑色係咪用armaflex呢。<br />\n仲有佢包鑽一個牆窿，其他店大約要加300蚊，如果你咁啱要鑽，又用盡15尺喉就還可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我假設佢msy gs09 賣4280, 即係安裝（不加鋁架）要$3000 ，但仲有啲收費未包架<br />\n避震膠冇寫唔知包唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆舊機封玻璃又冇寫幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n造架又冇寫幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果其他店分開計，<br />\n1匹基本安裝1600<br />\n電線入膠喉200<br />\n鑽牆窿300（唔係個個鑽）<br />\n<br />\n結論: 偏貴"},{"pid":"0c5762e0d847a072e246e61d31ec53a46853989d","tid":2504944,"uid":144182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"725b9fb07ae6d8d63edd40fcacae0410ce69f5bd","tid":2504944,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30c4ac6f742d17184bafe284b762e1d62fdc4e9f","tid":2504944,"uid":159294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3dc16ae7cf89ae140d70555e65cb1e854a6c6be","tid":2504944,"uid":144182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r